# Pre-push hook multi-mirror dedup cache (advisory; recreated on demand).
# Forensic anchor: SP-3a Step 6+7 used --no-verify on 3-of-4 mirror
# pushes because re-running scripts/ci.sh --changed-only against an
# identical SHA was redundant. The hook now caches verified SHAs in
# this file and skips Layer 2 on cache hit. Local-only by design.
.lava-ci-evidence/.pre-push-verified-shas
